channel.title: Sneak peak?
channel.description:
I am going to show you a little sneak peak to my server and client, and if you can't promise to post only good things then just leave, I don't really wanna here about how I leeched you when i didn't and i am giving the cred's so just look and see. This is just really a little sneak peak so I'm not going to list every feature, that will be when i release next week. I will be releasing the client and server next week maybe Tuesday. first pic is client loading and the second is logging on server. AND PLEASE DON"T STEAL MY IDEA OF THE BACKGROUND.
CLIENT

CREDS GO TO, I owner I for base of server
RIC for base of client
Now remember, I would like if you DON'T post anything bad.
